          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Inset, Undermount & Flushmount Kitchen Sinks",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_NfTz3m": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Choosing the right sink style is a defining decision when designing your dream kitchen. Inset, undermount, and flushmount sinks each bring distinct design characteristics, practical benefits, and aesthetic enhancements. Whether you're refreshing your space or planning a full renovation, explore our expertly selected sink styles below to find the perfect fit for your kitchen layout and design vision.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_8xnAD3",
