    "rich_text_7YiDix": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_HLPWrc": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/inset-sinks\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/inset-sinks\">Inset Sinks</a></h2>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_aDLzMN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Inset sinks, also known as top-mount sinks, are installed from above the benchtop, making them one of the most accessible and versatile sink styles available. Their visible lip creates a framed look that works well in both traditional and contemporary kitchen settings. Easy to install and often more budget-friendly, inset sinks are a popular choice for homeowners wanting a practical and stylish upgrade.</p><p>Designed to stand out, inset sinks offer flexibility in size and finish, accommodating a wide range of kitchen benchtops and configurations. Their elevated rim also acts as a barrier to water overflow, which can be especially useful in busy kitchens or family homes.<br/></p><ul><li>Simple to install with standard cabinetry</li><li>Visually frames the sink for a bold design statement</li><li>Edge lip helps contain spills and water</li><li>Compatible with laminate and stone benchtops</li><li>Ideal for renovations and retrofits</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_HLPWrc",
        "text_aDLzMN"
      ],
