    "rich_text_U9xNNy": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_zXwpWb": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/undermount\" title=\"Undermount Sink Collection\">Undermount Sinks</a></h2>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_LBd7gE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For a sleek and seamless aesthetic, undermount sinks are a favourite among design-conscious renovators and luxury kitchen planners. These sinks are mounted beneath the benchtop, allowing for an uninterrupted surface that’s both modern and functional. Without the lip of a top-mount sink, the bench appears more expansive and uncluttered, letting your materials — like stone or engineered quartz — shine.</p><p>Undermount sinks make cleaning easier too — simply wipe crumbs or water directly into the bowl without obstruction. They are ideal for minimalist designs and premium kitchen spaces where attention to detail matters.</p><p></p><ul><li>Seamless integration beneath benchtop</li><li>Maximise usable bench space and create visual flow</li><li>Easy wipe-down surface and with no sink lip interference</li><li>Perfect for modern, minimalist or luxury kitchens</li><li>Best suited to solid surface materials like stone</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
