    "rich_text_JWX8NY": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_kxezJx": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/flushmount\" title=\"Flushmount Sink collection\">Flushmount Sinks</a></h2>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_TiaVw3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Flushmount sinks offer the ultimate in design cohesion, sitting level with the benchtop for a perfectly integrated look. Whether used in contemporary designer kitchens or commercial-grade chef setups, flushmount sinks achieve a refined, architectural feel. The transition from sink to surface is seamless, both visually and functionally, enhancing the sophistication of the kitchen space.</p><p>Flushmount sinks are also easy to maintain, with no exposed edges or gaps where grime can accumulate. This makes them ideal for homeowners prioritising hygiene and clean lines without sacrificing bold design impact.</p><ul><li>Flat, flush fit with surrounding benchtop for seamless appeal</li><li>Highly hygenic with no ridges or crevices</li><li>Blends harmoniously with contemporary kitchen surfaces</li><li>Delivers a premium architectural finish</li><li>Often featured in designer and high-end homes</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
